      <b style="color: #1245BC; font-size: 11px;font-weight: bold;">Mission Activities: Mexico Mission, Native American Mission, Neighborhood Mission, India Mission, Light to Life</b>
    </div>
    <div style="padding-left:150px;">
      <b style="color: #a31010; font-size: 14px;font-style: italic;">'Reaching out to the unreached with the message of love'</b>
